'''Raijin Shrine''' (雷神社, Ikazuchi-jinja, Raijin-jinja, Kaminari-jinja) refers to Shinto shrines located throughout Japan.== Hokkaidō and Tōhoku Region ==* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Daisen)|ja|雷神社 (大仙市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Daisen|ja|大仙市}}, {{ill|Akita Prefecture|ja|秋田県}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Kaminoyama)|ja|雷神社 (上山市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Kaminoyama|ja|上山市}}, {{ill|Yamagata Prefecture|ja|山形県}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Kaneyama, Yamagata)|ja|雷神社 (山形県金山町)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Kaneyama, Mogami District|ja|金山町 (山形県)}}, Mogami District, Yamagata Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Kawanishi, Yamagata)|ja|雷神社 (山形県川西町)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Kawanishi, Higashiokitama District|ja|川西町 (山形県)}}, Higashiokitama District, Yamagata Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Shirataka)|ja|雷神社 (白鷹町)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Shirataka, Nishiokitama District|ja|白鷹町}}, Nishiokitama District, Yamagata Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Fukushima)|ja|雷神社 (福島市)}} - Located in {{ill|Fukushima|ja|福島市}}, {{ill|Fukushima Prefecture|ja|福島県}}, at Ōtamachi 7.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Fukushima)|ja|雷神社 (福島市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Another location in Fukushima City, at Okabemachi Uchi.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Kōriyama)|ja|雷神社 (郡山市)}} (Kaminari-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Kōriyama|ja|郡山市}}, Fukushima Prefecture, at Narukami 3-chōme.* {{ill|Asaka Raijin Shrine|ja|安積雷神社 (郡山市)}} (Asaka Kaminari-jinja) - Located in Kōriyama, at Hosonuma-chō.== Kantō Region ==* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Chikusei)|ja|雷神社 (筑西市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Chikusei|ja|筑西市}}, {{ill|Ibaraki Prefecture|ja|茨城県}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Utsunomiya)|ja|御蔵山古墳#雷神社}} (Ikazuchi-jinja/Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Utsunomiya|ja|宇都宮市}}, {{ill|Tochigi Prefecture|ja|栃木県}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Nagareyama)|ja|雷神社 (流山市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Nagareyama|ja|流山市}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Chiba City)|ja|雷神社 (千葉市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Chiba|ja|千葉市}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Ichihara)|ja|雷神社 (市原市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Ichihara|ja|市原市}}, Chiba Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Katori)|ja|雷神社 (香取市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Katori|ja|香取市}}, Chiba Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Asahi City)|ja|雷神社 (旭市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Asahi|ja|旭市}}, Chiba Prefecture.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Narita)|ja|雷神社 (成田市)}} (Raijin-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Narita|ja|成田市}}, Chiba Prefecture, at Yamaguchi 1205. Annual festival held on July 24.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Adachi)|ja|雷神社 (足立区)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Adachi|ja|足立区}}, {{ill|Tokyo Metropolis|ja|東京都}}, in Nishiarai.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Yokosuka)|ja|雷神社 (横須賀市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Yokosuka|ja|横須賀市}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県}}.== Hokuriku, Kōshin, Tōkai Region and Beyond ==* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Toyooka)|ja|雷神社 (豊岡市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Toyooka, Hyōgo|ja|豊岡市}}, {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県}}. A {{ill|Myōjin Taisha|ja|名神大社|式内名神大社}}.* {{ill|Raijin Shrine (Itoshima)|ja|雷神社 (糸島市)}} (Ikazuchi-jinja) - Located in {{ill|Itoshima|ja|糸島市}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県}}.== Related Articles ==* {{ill|Raiden Shrine|ja|雷電神社}}* ]][[:en:Ikazuchi|Ikazuchi]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrine]]]][[Category:Raijin Shrines]]]][[Category:bump]]]][[Category:File]]]][[Category:attempting to force refresh]]]][[Category:Shrine disambiguations]]
